project.title: Free Read, 1994 October 1 [FF0043-2]
project.description: Poetry Free Read at the 1994 Furious Flower Conference. The Free Read was held at Grafton-Stovall Theatre, James Madison University on Saturday, October 1, 1994. This footage was originally recorded on a MII videocassette.
